{"title":"Chamber of (data) secrets","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Chamber of (data) secrets","subtitle":"A blog by Edun Joshua","comments":false,"listing":{"feed":true,"contents":"posts/*/index.qmd","sort":"date desc","type":"grid","grid-columns":3,"image-height":"250px","page-size":100,"categories":true},"page-layout":"full","title-block-banner":true,"image":"profile.JPEG"},"headingText":"list names of post folders","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n```{r write-redirects}\n#| echo: false\nposts <- list.dirs(\n  path = here::here(\"posts\"),\n  full.names = FALSE,\n  recursive = FALSE\n)\n\n# extract the slugs\nslugs <- gsub(\"^.*_\", \"\", posts)\n\n# lines to insert to a netlify _redirect file\npost_redirects <- paste0(\"/\", slugs, \" \", \"/posts/\", posts)\n\n# function to extract post categories from index.qmd files\nget_post_categories <- function(post) {\n  file <- here::here(\"posts\", post) |> fs::path(\"index.qmd\")\n\t\n  if(!fs::file_exists(file)) {\n    return(character(0))\n  }\n  file |>\n    readLines(warn=FALSE) |> \n    stringr::str_subset(\"^categories:\") |>\n    stringr::str_extract(\"\\\\[.*\\\\]\") |> \n    stringr::str_remove_all(\"[\\\\[\\\\]]\") |>\n    stringr::str_split(\", \") |> \n    unlist()\n}\n\n# extract the categories\ncategories <- purrr::map(posts, get_post_categories) |> \n  unlist() |> \n  unique()\n\n# extract categories in nice form\nkeys <- categories |> \n  stringr::str_to_lower() |>\n  stringr::str_replace_all(\" \", \"-\")\n\n# extract categories in ugly form\nvalues <- categories |>\n  stringr::str_replace_all(\" \", \"%20\")\n\n# category redirects\ncategory_redirects <- paste0(\"/category/\", keys, \" \", \"/#category=\", values)\n\n# write the _redirect file\nwriteLines(c(post_redirects, category_redirects), here::here(\"_site\", \"_redirects\"))\n```\n\n<!-- Mastodon verification -->\n<!-- <a rel=\"me\" style=\"display:none\" href=\"https://fosstodon.org/@djnavarro\">Hidden link used to verify my account on fosstodon.org</a>  -->\n<!-- <a rel=\"me\" style=\"display:none\" href=\"https://genart.social/@djnavarro\">Hidden link used to verify my account on genart.social</a> -->\n<!-- <a rel=\"me\" style=\"display:none\" href=\"https://hachyderm.io/@djnavarro\">Hidden link used to verify my account on hachyderm.io</a>  -->\n\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n```{r write-redirects}\n#| echo: false\n# list names of post folders\nposts <- list.dirs(\n  path = here::here(\"posts\"),\n  full.names = FALSE,\n  recursive = FALSE\n)\n\n# extract the slugs\nslugs <- gsub(\"^.*_\", \"\", posts)\n\n# lines to insert to a netlify _redirect file\npost_redirects <- paste0(\"/\", slugs, \" \", \"/posts/\", posts)\n\n# function to extract post categories from index.qmd files\nget_post_categories <- function(post) {\n  file <- here::here(\"posts\", post) |> fs::path(\"index.qmd\")\n\t\n  if(!fs::file_exists(file)) {\n    return(character(0))\n  }\n  file |>\n    readLines(warn=FALSE) |> \n    stringr::str_subset(\"^categories:\") |>\n    stringr::str_extract(\"\\\\[.*\\\\]\") |> \n    stringr::str_remove_all(\"[\\\\[\\\\]]\") |>\n    stringr::str_split(\", \") |> \n    unlist()\n}\n\n# extract the categories\ncategories <- purrr::map(posts, get_post_categories) |> \n  unlist() |> \n  unique()\n\n# extract categories in nice form\nkeys <- categories |> \n  stringr::str_to_lower() |>\n  stringr::str_replace_all(\" \", \"-\")\n\n# extract categories in ugly form\nvalues <- categories |>\n  stringr::str_replace_all(\" \", \"%20\")\n\n# category redirects\ncategory_redirects <- paste0(\"/category/\", keys, \" \", \"/#category=\", values)\n\n# write the _redirect file\nwriteLines(c(post_redirects, category_redirects), here::here(\"_site\", \"_redirects\"))\n```\n\n<!-- Mastodon verification -->\n<!-- <a rel=\"me\" style=\"display:none\" href=\"https://fosstodon.org/@djnavarro\">Hidden link used to verify my account on fosstodon.org</a>  -->\n<!-- <a rel=\"me\" style=\"display:none\" href=\"https://genart.